snippet.textDisplay: I'm surprised why Coke Studio India doesn't get many Punjabi singers. With such awesome meaningful lyrics and foot tapping music, their songs are a treat to both eyes and ears. If I'm able to reach out to Coke Studio, I'd like to request that please bring more of Punjabi folk singers like Gurdas Maan Ji and do not waste an episode with a single music producer who in turn offers too many lackluster songs. Bring Season 1 format back!
snippet.textOriginal: I'm surprised why Coke Studio India doesn't get many Punjabi singers. With such awesome meaningful lyrics and foot tapping music, their songs are a treat to both eyes and ears. If I'm able to reach out to Coke Studio, I'd like to request that please bring more of Punjabi folk singers like Gurdas Maan Ji and do not waste an episode with a single music producer who in turn offers too many lackluster songs. Bring Season 1 format back!
